column2: select * from openquery ([#.#], #'gbm_tcga# union all select p.stable_id , cam.attr_id, cls.attr_value from cancer_study cs inner join clinical_attribute_meta cam on cam.cancer_study_id = cs.cancer_study_id and cam.patient_attribute = # inner join patient p on p.cancer_study_id = cs.cancer_study_id inner join sample s on s.patient_id = p.internal_id inner join clinical_sample cls on s.internal_id = cls.internal_id and cls.attr_id = cam.attr_id where cs.cancer_study_identifier = #gbm_tcga#') a
